                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for producing hydrogen by reforming low-carbon fuel moving bed",
                    "一种低碳燃料移动床重整制氢的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of hydrogen production processes, and discloses a method for hydrogen production by reforming of a low-carbon fuel moving bed reactor. According to the method, a moving bed reactor is adopted as a place for reforming hydrogen production, solid particles are fed from the top of the reactor, fuel is fed from the bottom of the reactor, technological condition optimization is performed by adjusting the steam-carbon ratio and the calcium-ring ratio, full reaction is performed in a gas-solid countercurrent contact mode, and high-purity hydrogen is prepared. And meanwhile, the system realizes self-heating operation due to heat absorption and release reaction in the reactor. According to the invention, a gas-solid countercurrent moving bed reactor is introduced for reforming reaction, the limitation of thermodynamic equilibrium in a single-stage gasification reactor in traditional reforming hydrogen production is broken through, the defect of complex operation of a process unit in existing hydrogen production is overcome, and gt; the hydrogen purity is 90%, and effective integration after simplification of multi-unit operation process design under the condition that the high hydrogen purity is guaranteed provides a new method and way for enhancing reforming reaction to prepare high-purity hydrogen."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于制氢工艺技术领域，公开了一种低碳燃料移动床反应器重整制氢的方法。该方法采用移动床反应器作为重整制氢的场所，固体颗粒从反应器顶部进料，燃料在从反应器底部进料，并通过调节汽碳比和钙环比进行工艺条件优化，以气固逆流的接触方式充分反应，制得高纯度的氢气，同时反应器中存在的吸放热反应使系统实现自热运行。本发明提出引入气固逆流移动床反应器进行重整反应，突破传统重整制氢存在的单级气化反应器中热力学平衡的限制以及克服现有制氢存在的工艺单元操作复杂的不足，实现>90％的氢气纯度和保证较高氢气纯度下多单元操作工艺设计简化之后的有效集成，为加强重整反应制高纯度氢气提供了新的方法和途径。"
                }
            ]
